         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. Garden ¶ 9/9/64. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to solicit that you will be pleased to advance to me from the treasury the sum of thirty pounds sterling (£30.- .-), which amount you ¶  ¶ d...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">64.09.09</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James McCulloch</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">K64/9168, unit 49, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne bot. Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">9/9/64.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to solicit that you will be pleased to advance to me from the treasury the sum of thirty pounds sterling (£30.- .-), which amount you<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>desired me to expend in procuring seeds of forest trees in this country for the Madras Government.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>On 26 August 1864, the Governor's office had written to M to authorize a sum of £30 to be spent on seeds for Madras (letter not found; acknowledged in M to H. Warde, 27 August 1864).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>On 14 September 1864, the Under Secretary, J. Moore, minuted 'The Director of the Botanic Gardens is informed that the sum he requires will be advanced to him by the Treasury on his signing the enclosed application and returning it to this office'. M returned the application the next day adding: 'Signed accordingly with thanks'; Moore instructed: 'Advance application for £30 counter signed and forwarded to the Honble the Treasurer'. On 29 September 1864, E. S.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Symonds minuted:<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'Returned<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to the Under Secy — The advance act. [account] has been<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>posted<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for payment'.</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The availability of the seeds for shipment was notified to J. McCulloch, 12 September 1864 (in this edition as 64-09-12b).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M.D.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable the Chief Secretary</p>
